{"tid":1840064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯求租35歲前曼聯殺星回歸","createTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T12:25:13.000Z","uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e4742db800c0f0779bf0509b8689509b41f17a","tid":1840064,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"拉舒福特（Marcus Rashford）重傷之後，曼聯的進攻點火力缺乏，蘇斯克查（Ole Solskj&aelig;r）在排兵佈陣上可以說是捉襟見肘。於是，在冬季轉會窗關閉之前找到一名前鋒成了當務之急。<br />\n<br />\n  來自《都靈體育報》的消息透露，活禾特（Edward Woodward）竟然看上了現年35歲的前曼聯殺星泰維斯（Carlos Tevez），該報稱，鑒於泰維斯和目前的東家小保加之間的合約將在今年6月份到期，所以曼聯想要租借泰維斯半年應急，直到今季結束。<br />\n<br />\n  阿根廷老將泰維斯曾經在2007年至2009年期間效力於曼聯，但是他與時任曼聯主教練的費格遜（Alex Ferguson）關係破裂，隨後他加盟了曼聯的同城死敵曼城，但是令曼聯球迷無法忘卻的是，2012年泰維斯隨曼城奪取英超冠軍之後，他竟然舉起了印有「R.I.P - Fergie」（費格遜安息）的牌，這一舉動讓曼聯球迷忍無可忍，痛罵他為「反骨仔」！<br />\n<br />\n  很難想像，如果泰維斯重返奧脫福，那麼曼聯的球迷會如何對待他？"},{"pid":"eb312a1a84a4c633dfffb0881e54a1a9b56d2e87","tid":1840064,"uid":301668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"this one funny<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e7865deeb050460b495e0269bc98973ec0a950","tid":1840064,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:44:38.000Z","msg":"R.I.P - Fergie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457289fe7694109c7d9b6fa6dc4b98d58fb452db","tid":1840064,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"35歲阿朗呢"},{"pid":"d71aaa3e3b469f8b3a4bd6913a6d36c8c1d7dbb2","tid":1840064,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"買埋朗尼同c朗返黎"},{"pid":"ccd3dcd8c79afa7bcfce7695791524b54bbfcbbd","tid":1840064,"uid":66536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d71aaa3e3b469f8b3a4bd6913a6d36c8c1d7dbb2","tid":1840064,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply